item.title: KOSS
item.description: We are a group of volunteer students at IIT Kharagpur who promote Open Source. To get more beginners introduced to Open Source, we hold events like Kharagpur Winter of Code Ubuntu Install Fest Version control (Git + GitHub workflow) Various workshops Python Classes Golang Classes Javascript classes Android Development Hackathons Read more about our Events.
